.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
.fuse_hidden*
.directory
.Trash-*

# --- OPENTOFU / TERRAFORM ---
**/.terraform/
# Glob covers terraform.tfstate, .backup, and timestamped backups (.<ts>.backup).
*.tfstate*
